variant_descriptions.KXNORW: Bitwise XNOR 16-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KXNORB: Bitwise XNOR 8-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KXNORQ: Bitwise XNOR 64-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KXNORD: Bitwise XNOR 32-bit masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.

op.text: Performs a bitwise XNOR between the vector mask k2 and the vector mask k3, and writes the result into vector mask k1 (three-operand form).
